---
import Site from '../../../layouts/Site.astro';
---
<Site title={'about — rega rega'}>
<Fragment set:html={'<div class="meta-top">\n  <div class="crumbs">\n    <span class="cur"><span class="dot"></span>about</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<section class="head">\n  <div class="inner">\n    <h1>two paths<br/>that <em>met</em>.</h1>\n    <p class="lede"><b>Two paths that met in Batumi.</b> One started managing apartments by accident. The other was looking for a market like this to build something properly.</p>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section class="story">\n  <div class="inner">\n    <p><span class="drop">O</span>lga arrived in Batumi at the very start of 2022. Before that, she\'d been a project manager at <b>«Сделано»</b>, a Moscow startup — and along the way she\'d accumulated something rare: real, hands-on experience setting up apartments across half a dozen cities she\'d lived in. She knew the smell of new sheets, the weight of a properly hemmed curtain, the difference between a kitchen that photographs well and one that lives well.</p>\n    <p>In Batumi she came to help with flowers — the natural continuation of <b>Plant Me</b>, her plant studio in Moscow. But within months an owner asked her to manage his flat. Then his friend asked. Then a neighbour. The thing she\'d been doing as a hobby across her own homes turned out to be exactly what people in Batumi needed and nobody was doing properly.</p>\n\n    <h3>then <em>artem</em>.</h3>\n\n    <p><span class="drop">A</span>rtem joined later. He\'d spent years between cities — <b>real estate, brand launches, investment work</b>, the kind of life that puts you in a different hotel almost every week. After enough of those nights you stop being a guest and start being a critic: the towel weight, the lighting temperature, the receipt waiting at checkout, the small things that separate a good operator from a bad one. He knew this language fluently — from the customer side.</p>\n    <p>He was looking for someone to build it with. A market where the demand was real, the standards were low, and the team was the bottleneck. When he found Olya already running ten apartments on her own, the conversation was short.</p>\n\n    <h3>two halves, <em>one product</em>.</h3>\n\n    <p>The interesting part isn\'t that we\'re partners. It\'s that we come from <em>opposite sides of the room</em> — Olya from operations and the inside of a home, Artem from strategy and the outside view of how systems behave. One built things by hand for a decade. The other watched things being built and saw what was missing.</p>\n    <p>Together we\'re building what we think the region has been missing: <b>the best property operator in Batumi</b>. Honest about money, ruthless about quality, small on purpose. Built one apartment at a time, one owner at a time. Slow on purpose. Right by default.</p>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section class="people">\n  <div class="container">\n    <div class="people-head">\n      <div class="kicker"><span class="dot"></span>— who\'s behind this</div>\n      <h2>two <em>halves</em>,<br/>one operation.</h2>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class="profiles">\n      <div class="profile">\n        <div class="ph">\n          <img src="https://static.tildacdn.one/tild3861-3030-4661-a262-316335653632/photo_2024-06-13_121.jpeg" alt="Olya, co-founder of bre" onerror="this.src=\'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?w=900&q=80\'">\n        </div>\n        <div class="role"><span class="sw"></span>co-founder · people &amp; operations</div>\n        <h3><em>olya</em></h3>\n        <p class="bio">Founder of <b>Plant Me</b>, a Moscow plant studio. Years of hands-on apartment setup across cities — knows textiles, lighting, the rhythm of a home.</p>\n        <p class="bio">At bre she runs <b>guests, standards, and the quality bar</b>. Every apartment we take on passes through her hands.</p>\n        <div class="does">\n          <div class="row">guest hosting</div>\n          <div class="row">the bre standard</div>\n          <div class="row">cleaning &amp; quality control</div>\n          <div class="row">supplier relations</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class="links">\n          <a href="https://t.me/bre_ge">↗ telegram</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class="profile">\n        <div class="ph">\n          <img src="https://www.grinbergart.com/assets/artem-hero-clean.png" alt="Artem, co-founder of bre">\n        </div>\n        <div class="role"><span class="sw"></span>co-founder · strategy &amp; infrastructure</div>\n        <h3><em>artem</em></h3>\n        <p class="bio">Spent years <b>launching tech-driven businesses and developing real estate</b>. Lives between cities — knows hospitality from the customer side, after enough hotel nights to be hard to impress.</p>\n        <p class="bio">At bre he runs <b>strategy, owner relations, sales, and the platform underneath</b>: the bookkeeping system, the new product ideas.</p>\n        <div class="does">\n          <div class="row">strategy &amp; positioning</div>\n          <div class="row">owner &amp; investor relations</div>\n          <div class="row">infrastructure &amp; tooling</div>\n          <div class="row">sales &amp; deal sourcing</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class="links">\n          <a href="https://grinbergart.com">↗ grinbergart.com</a>\n          <a href="https://t.me/grinbergart">↗ telegram</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section class="mission">\n  <blockquote>we want to build<br/>the <em>best property operator</em><br/>in the region.</blockquote>\n  <div class="signoff">— our north star, since 2022</div>\n</section>\n\n<section class="cta-wrap">\n  <h2>now you <em>know us</em>.<br/>say hi.</h2>\n  <p>Book a stay, list your flat, ask a question. We work from a small office in the old town and we like meeting people in person.</p>\n  <div class="row">\n    <a class="btn primary" href="https://t.me/bre_ge">↗ message on telegram</a>\n    <a class="btn alt" href="tel:+995585889601">+995 585 889 601</a>\n  </div>\n</section>'} />
<style is:global set:html={'.meta-top{padding:96px 28px 16px;font-family:"JetBrains Mono",monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-soft);font-weight:500;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}\n.meta-top .crumbs{display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap}\n.meta-top .crumbs a:hover{color:var(--ink)}\n.meta-top .crumbs .sep{opacity:.4}\n.meta-top .crumbs .cur{color:var(--page-deep);font-weight:700;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;background:var(--accent-soft);padding:5px 11px;border-radius:999px}\n.meta-top .crumbs .cur .dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--page)}\n.head{padding:64px 28px 80px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}\n.head .inner{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto}\n.head h1{font-family:"Bricolage Grotesque",sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(56px,8vw,140px);line-height:.88;letter-spacing:-.045em;text-transform:lowercase;max-width:18ch}\n.head h1 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--page)}\n.head .lede{font-family:"Newsreader",Georgia,serif;font-style:italic;font-size:clamp(20px,2.2vw,28px);line-height:1.5;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-top:36px;max-width:36ch;font-weight:400}\n.head .lede b{color:var(--ink);font-weight:500;font-style:normal}\n.story{padding:80px 28px}\n.story .inner{max-width:680px;margin:0 auto}\n.story p{font-family:"Newsreader",Georgia,serif;font-size:19px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:20px;font-weight:400}\n.story p b{font-weight:600}\n.story p em{font-style:italic;color:var(--page)}\n.story .drop{font-family:"Bricolage Grotesque",sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:64px;line-height:.85;letter-spacing:-.04em;color:var(--page);float:left;margin-right:14px;margin-top:8px}\n.story h3{font-family:"Bricolage Grotesque",sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:32px;letter-spacing:-.03em;text-transform:lowercase;margin:48px 0 20px;line-height:1}\n.story h3 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--page)}\n.people{padding:96px 28px;background:var(--paper);border-top:1px solid var(--line);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}\n.people .container{max-width:1400px;margin:0 auto}\n.people-head{margin-bottom:48px;max-width:600px}\n.people-head .kicker{font-family:"JetBrains Mono",monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--page-deep);font-weight:600;margin-bottom:18px;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:var(--accent-soft);padding:5px 11px;border-radius:999px;width:fit-content}\n.people-head .kicker .dot{display:none}\n.people-head h2{font-family:"Bricolage Grotesque",sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(40px,5.5vw,82px);line-height:.95;letter-spacing:-.04em;text-transform:lowercase}\n.people-head h2 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--page)}\n.profiles{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:32px}\n.profile{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:18px;padding:32px;background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:14px;transition:border-color .25s ease}\n.profile:hover{border-color:var(--page)}\n.profile .ph{aspect-ratio:1;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;background:var(--bg-2);position:relative}\n.profile .ph img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover}\n.profile .role{font-family:"JetBrains Mono",monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-soft);font-weight:600;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}\n.profile .role .sw{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--page)}\n.profile h3{font-family:"Bricolage Grotesque",sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:36px;letter-spacing:-.03em;text-transform:lowercase;line-height:1}\n.profile h3 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--page)}\n.profile .bio{font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--ink-soft)}\n.profile .bio b{color:var(--ink);font-weight:600}\n.profile .does{padding-top:14px;border-top:1px solid var(--line);font-family:"JetBrains Mono",monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink);font-weight:600;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px}\n.profile .does .row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}\n.profile .does .row::before{content:"";width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--page);flex:none}\n.profile .links{display:flex;gap:14px;font-family:"JetBrains Mono",monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink-soft)}\n.profile .links a:hover{color:var(--page)}\n.mission{padding:120px 28px;background:var(--ink);color:#fff;text-align:center}\n.mission blockquote{font-family:"Bricolage Grotesque",sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(38px,5.5vw,72px);line-height:1.05;letter-spacing:-.04em;text-transform:lowercase;max-width:24ch;margin:0 auto}\n.mission blockquote em{font-style:italic;color:var(--page)}\n.mission .signoff{margin-top:32px;font-family:"JetBrains Mono",monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#ffffff77;font-weight:500}\n.cta-wrap{padding:120px 28px;text-align:center;border-top:1px solid var(--line)}\n.cta-wrap h2{font-family:"Bricolage Grotesque",sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(44px,6vw,96px);line-height:.95;letter-spacing:-.04em;text-transform:lowercase;max-width:18ch;margin:0 auto 24px}\n.cta-wrap h2 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--page)}\n.cta-wrap p{max-width:42ch;margin:0 auto 36px;font-size:17px;line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink-soft)}\n.cta-wrap .row{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap}\n.btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:18px 28px;border-radius:999px;font-family:"JetBrains Mono",monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:700;transition:all .25s ease;border:1px solid transparent}\n.btn.primary{background:var(--ink);color:#fff}\n.btn.primary:hover{background:var(--page);color:#fff}\n.btn.alt{background:transparent;color:var(--ink);border-color:var(--ink)}\n.btn.alt:hover{background:var(--ink);color:#fff}\n@media (max-width:880px){\n.head{padding:64px 14px 48px}\n.head h1{font-size:clamp(40px,11vw,64px)}\n.head .lede{font-size:18px}\n.story{padding:48px 18px}\n.story p{font-size:17.5px}\n.people{padding:48px 14px}\n.profiles{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:16px}\n.profile{padding:22px}\n.mission{padding:64px 14px}\n.cta-wrap{padding:56px 14px}\n}'}></style>
</Site>
